<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我们要把旧蜡笔变成彩虹蜡烛。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拿起一个彩色的蜡烛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜看了看自己的旧蜡笔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31151</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她不确定要不要把紫色蜡笔放到彩虹蜡烛里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“首先，我们看看有什么颜色。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42775</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们都拿出了蜡笔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53049</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们有红色、橙色、黄色、蓝色、绿色……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53049</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58010</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有很多尼娜拿来的紫色！” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“刚好可以做彩虹蜡烛。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜举起手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪莉老师，我可以做个紫色的蜡烛吗？我不想要彩虹蜡烛。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师想了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73492</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，我们要分享蜡笔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你只想要紫色，蜡烛就会很短。那样可以吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82900</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88814</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜点点头。“是的，只要是紫色就行。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88814</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好。首先，我们要把蜡笔上的纸撕掉。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“蜡烛里不能有纸。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106663</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们做好之后，雪莉老师点起电炉的火。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106663</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我们要让蜡笔融化。一次一个颜色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们要把它们放在锅里融化。” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116822</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请放红色的蜡笔。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们把红色蜡笔放进锅里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，它们开始融化了！” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小心。锅很烫！” 雪莉老师提醒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我们把蜡倒进玻璃罐里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>像这样小心地把烛芯放在罐子中间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我来倒蜡。不要把烛芯放开！” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159675</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她倒了一层红色的蜡到莉琪、贾森和波比的罐子底下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159675</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后她又倒了橙色、黄色、绿色和蓝色的蜡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜看着。她的罐子还是空的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172150</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了。最后一层。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176955</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜跳起来，拿起她的罐子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184294</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>紫色终于准备好了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184294</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师给每个人都倒了一些紫色的蜡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪莉老师，我的蜡烛太短了。” 尼娜皱着眉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“尼娜，我刚才告诉过你了。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道。但我不知道它会是这个样子！” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她伤心地看着她的短蜡烛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我还有一些红色的蜡笔。” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贾森有蓝色的蜡笔。红色和蓝色混合起来是紫色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226840</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们可以做更多紫色的蜡。” 波比看着雪莉老师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜对波比笑了笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238162</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238162</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有时候波比还挺亲切的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们把红色和蓝色的蜡笔一起放进锅里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254057</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得这样就可以了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261814</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你觉得呢？” 雪莉老师问尼娜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261814</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜的蜡烛没有彩虹蜡烛那么高。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但已经快要装满罐子了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，好多了。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>之后雪莉老师剪断大家的烛芯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279993</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她点亮蜡烛，关上灯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284610</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家的蜡烛都在黑暗中发着光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289215</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的蜡烛看上去真不错！” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293456</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的彩虹蜡烛真漂亮。” 尼娜对莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢。你的紫色蜡烛也很漂亮。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在烛光中，尼娜看着儿童中心的老师和朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她和他们在一起很幸福！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>